"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Better to have the skills of a legendary poker player than to simply run good for a few years.\\n\\nSo what do I want to be at the end of this growth process? What’s the description of my skills, who I am?\\n\\n* healthy\\n* an effortless wealth-generator\\n  * my skill level and systems are so excellent that earning wild chunks of capital happens essentially of its own accord\\n    * artful blend of quant and discretionary, generically applicable to any endeavor involving risk or warfighting\\n\\nMy latest approach to (1) engaging in focused work to accomplish a singular goal while (2) satisfying my curiosity and the explorative side of the multi-armed bandit problem is through following these basic heuristics:\\n\\n1. health\\n2. focus\\n3. simple\\n\\nAs long as, every day, I do quality work on these three things, the rest of my time can be spent on whatever random curiosity I want.\\n\\nHealth is the top priority because, like it or not, physical wellbeing is the foundation of everything else in my life.\\n\\nNow is my time to concentrate on winning the wealth game in order to attain socioeconomic independence, to get a seat at the poker table of capitalists. Focused work on my trading systems and investing in myself, with a bias towards simplicity, is what I’ve identified as the most effective non-ergodic play.\",\"timestamp\":1638394382,\"title\":\"concentration and dispersion\"},\"digest\":\"tf-uIJeaFsQMgKsgGzaXxM4XHz7xWn3vWrIunDxsho4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xdF3AB3adB9F679d71b9A22ab77565b1FF3A5047D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"_JiuWO731F3bhDAPMgNFNaovDkRTPSt89uP_9frEql4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bHF0APHB54AF9Lt0UPWhYOciyTUJwUKTBwpcE4mjYro\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jkP5LIUfrdxepaJvJGYXncN2pRL5GtEenGrwrmpdHZaYARM3T9Z7GNBHSLKD90Aslpup04AB9Gef7RgA8Il_Ng\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc5d28cfb46ae00586cde083af70323f43855092c0ab6403c20